, & \\text{for~} D> n^{1/3}~. \\end{cases} \\] We also\nextend our algorithms to provide improved $(\\beta,\\epsilon)$ hopsets for\n$n$-vertex weighted directed graphs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Nov 2021 20:25:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-29"}
