dius of the optimization domain. The key idea for proving the lower\nbound consists of perturbing the hard functions of Hamilton and Moitra (2021)\nwith sums of bump functions chosen by a resisting oracle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Nov 2021 21:54:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Jan 2022 00:54:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 6 Jun 2023 06:12:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
