lex manner with the change of\nthe anisotropy and the ferromagnetic or antiferromagnetic orders of the spins.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Nov 2021 00:06:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-03"}
