he particle\ndisplacement for a fixed time and its average drift velocity on each period of\nthe gradient magnetic field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Nov 2021 15:12:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Dec 2021 16:26:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-03"}
