uded that unlearning is considerably superior to retraining. Results show\nthat unlearning is fast, easy to implement, easy to use, and effective.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Nov 2021 12:13:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Dec 2021 16:48:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-28"}
